Auth: User logs in via Google OAuth (Supabase).

Load: App fetches profiles (points) and items (shop).

Interact: Alpine.js updates local state (Merchant reactions).

Transact: User clicks "Buy" -> Calls purchase_item RPC -> Updates DB.

Notify: DB Trigger fires Discord Webhook.

2. Key Components

The Portal (/): Simple HTML/CSS entry point.

The Shop (/shop/): Single Page Application (SPA) feel using standard HTML pages.

The Merchant: shop/js/app.js controls the sprite state based on user actions.

3. Server Config (Nginx)

Ensure Nginx is configured to serve static files from /shop:

location /shop {
    alias /var/www/joeyspace.dev/shop;
    index index.html;
    try_files $uri $uri/ =404;
}
